                            <p class="text-sm mt-0 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">Get detailed insights into test performance, flaky tests, and execution trends with comprehensive dashboards.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
